---
import WhatsAppButton from './WhatsAppButton.astro';
---
<section
  id="top"
  data-hero="wash-css"
  class="hero-offset-under-header hero-with-bottom-air scroll-mt-24 relative flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden hero-height"
  aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
>
  <div class="hero-scene" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src="/audience-adult.png"
      alt=""
      class="hero-scene__image"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
      decoding="async"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="hero-wash-grey" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-wash-navy" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-wash-gradient" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-5 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:px-12 xl:px-16">
    <div class="hero-unified-card" style="
    margin-top: 39%;
">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p
          class="hero-text-glow font-display mb-3 text-sm font-light tracking-wide text-brand-breath sm:mb-5 sm:text-base"
        >
          Precisión científica para tu bienestar diario.
        </p>
        <h1
          id="hero-heading"
          class="hero-text-glow font-display mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white sm:mb-6 sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
        >
          Recupera tu calidad de vida controlando tu alergia desde la raíz.
        </h1>
        <p
          class="hero-text-glow mb-6 max-w-2xl text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed text-white sm:mb-8 sm:text-xl"
        >
          Más de 20 años ayudando a niños y adultos en el NEA a vivir sin síntomas, con un enfoque médico
          integral.
        </p>
        <div>
          <WhatsAppButton>Quiero agendar mi consulta</WhatsAppButton>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <div class="hero-portrait-slot">
          <img
            src="/dr-liber-acosta-1920.png"
            srcset="/dr-liber-acosta-1920.png 1920w, /dr-liber-acosta-2880.png 2880w"
            alt="Foto del doctor"
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 420px, 0px"
            class="hero-portrait"
            width="1920"
            height="2400"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
